<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>VISUS AI Navigation</title>

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    background:#061321;
    color:white;
    overflow-x:hidden;
}

.hero{
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
}

.logo{
    width:280px;
    max-width:80%;
    margin-bottom:30px;
    z-index:10;
}

h1{
    font-size:4rem;
    letter-spacing:4px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
    z-index:10;
}

.tagline{
    font-size:1.4rem;
    color:#8bc6ff;
    margin-bottom:25px;
    z-index:10;
}

.description{
    max-width:700px;
    line-height:1.7;
    font-size:1.1rem;
    padding:0 20px;
    z-index:10;
}

.download-btn{
    margin-top:40px;
    padding:18px 40px;
    background:#008cff;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:40px;
    font-size:1.1rem;
    transition:0.3s;
    z-index:10;
}

.download-btn:hover{
    transform:scale(1.05);
}

.beam{
    position:absolute;
    width:900px;
    height:180px;

    background:linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        rgba(180,220,255,0.45),
        rgba(180,220,255,0.05),
        transparent
    );

    top:38%;
    left:50%;
    transform-origin:left center;

    animation:sweep 10s ease-in-out infinite;
    filter:blur(12px);
}

@keyframes sweep{

0%{
transform:rotate(-18deg);
}

50%{
transform:rotate(18deg);
}

100%{
transform:rotate(-18deg);
}

}

.features{
    padding:100px 20px;
    text-align:center;
    background:#081a2c;
}

.features h2{
    margin-bottom:60px;
    font-size:2.2rem;
}

.cards{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:30px;
}

.card{
    width:300px;
    padding:35px;
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius:18px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
}

.card h3{
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.roadmap{
    text-align:center;
    padding:100px 20px;
}

.roadmap h2{
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.roadmap ul{
    list-style:none;
    line-height:2;
}

footer{
    padding:40px;
    text-align:center;
    border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    color:#8aa7c0;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<section class="hero">

<div class="beam"></div>

<img src="visus-logo.png" class="logo">

<h1>VISUS AI</h1>

<p class="tagline">
Helping Skippers See Beyond The Horizon
</p>

<p class="description">
VISUS AI is an intelligent maritime navigation platform designed to enhance situational awareness and decision-making through advanced artificial intelligence models.
</p>

<a href="#" class="download-btn">
Download App
</a>

</section>

<section class="features">

<h2>Navigation Intelligence</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>AI Navigation</h3>
<p>
Advanced navigation assistance powered by artificial intelligence.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Intelligent Models</h3>
<p>
Marine intelligence models designed to improve route awareness.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Situational Awareness</h3>
<p>
Helping mariners make safer and smarter decisions at sea.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="roadmap">

<h2>Roadmap</h2>

<ul>
<li>✓ VISUS AI Navigation</li>
<li>✓ AI Maritime Models</li>
<li>⟳ Computer Vision Integration</li>
<li>⟳ VISUS AI Pro</li>
<li>⟳ Advanced Maritime Intelligence</li>
</ul>

</section>

<footer>

Powered by FrontSea Intelligence

</footer>

</body>
</html>
